race.comment: PLAY DIRTY (8) is on a hot streak of form, the latest charging out of the boxes early and scoring at this track (23.85), making it four straight wins. Boasts five wins from seven starts out of this box. Expected to go well again. GOLDEN ENVY (3) flew the lids from the middle with a slick turn of foot before finishing second (23.89) and beaten 5 lengths over 407m at this track. Bold showing expected. FARMOR BACARDI (2) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (21.96) at Townsville behind Total Franky in a Grade 3/4. Has the pace to be prominent. Expected to feature again. ZIPPITY ZEAL (4) must be respected at her pet track and distance.
